data.description: Nestled on a quiet cul de sac in South Forsyth this charming home on .60-acre level lot features a private, fenced backyard perfect for entertaining and family activities. NO HOA. Award winning school district. The updated kitchen showcases an expansive 11ft island, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances. Kitchen opens to the family room with marble fireplace and gas logs. Laundry with flex room off the kitchen. The 2-story entryway greets with an open staircase, formal dining room, private powder room, and a living room/office that joins the family room. The upstairs layout provides enough privacy for the whole family. The spacious master suite features a large bath with dual vanities, a soaking tub, separate shower & large walk-in closet. The remainder of the upstairs finishes with an additional “Master Size” bedroom, 2 walk-in closets, and a large unfinished walk-in attic, 2 additional bedrooms with walk-in closets and a full bath with tub/shower combination. CARPET ALLOWANCE FOR UPSTAIRS. Architectural shingle roof Feb 2021 and luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the main level and upstairs bathrooms.     Conveniently located minutes away from Vickery Village, One Life Fitness, The Big Creek Greenway, The Polo Fields, Midway Park, Halcyon and GA 400. Close to everything - yet so peaceful, this family friendly neighborhood hosts summer block parties and other holiday events.
